This test will check that krecipes can able to create a new recipe
<dl>
    <dt>Launch krecipes</dt>
        <dd>krecipes opens, a welcoming message will be displayed</dd>
    <!-- EAGER STEP -->
    <dt>Click on "Next" > select the database type and click on "Next" > Enter the db filename and click on "Next"</dt>
        <dd>Initialize Database screen will be displayed</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Next" > click on "Finish"</dt>
        <dd>Krecipes window will be opened</dd>
    <dt>Click on "New Recipe"</dt>
        <dd>Edit Recipe window will be opened</dd>
    <dt>Fill the informations in the "Recipe","Ingredients","Instructions" & "Ratings" tab > Click on "Save recipe" button</dt>
        <dd>The recipe is saved</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Show Recipe" button</dt>
        <dd>The new recipe will be displayed</dd>
</dl>

